            "遵循例子21之前的第一个过程的步骤:"
            (MB (deriv $beta
                       (tu0 $b_1 (&i* $2 $b_1) $b_3 (&+ (&i* $3 $b_1) (&i* $4 $b_3)) $b_5)
                       (&d* (Mat ($b_1 $b_3 $b_5 $0 $0)) $R)
                       (&d* (Mat ($b_1 $b_3 $b_5 $0 $0)) (&i* $P $A))
                       (&d* (&i* (Mat ($b_1 $b_3 $b_5 $0 $0))
